node.text: Y’all ain’t even ready. Y’all know I’m always on literally 100.. okay, maybe a little hyper. I LOVE life EVERYDAY!  I’m always jacked up on Jesus Red Bull. 🤣🤣 how bout, I done gone and fell overboard. Thank God it was me.. cause they can’t swim 😂😂😂😂 not one jumped in after me lol  this is my praise break today🙌🏼🔥👊🏼 enjoy and watch till the end 😆😆 no worries I didn’t hurt myself. I swam to the dock. I’ll show that video next. Everybody needs a friend like me... extra!!

node.text: 😂😂 yesssss! Walking into this week like….. walk walk walk! Y’all come on!! This is your praise break! You decide how this week is gonna be right… NOW! Get out of your comfort zone.. LIVE! Forgive! Let go! Move on!! Be a world changer!! #realtalkkim #tiktok #LIVEyourBESTlife #JoydowninmyBones #BeYourOwnHypeSquad #favormagnet #GodsGirl

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by REAL TALK KIM on July 26, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'YOU CAN COMEBACK FROM ANYTHING NO MATTER HOW BAD IT IS! SHIFT YOUR THINKING To BELIEVE IN YOU AGAIN!'.

node.text: Facts!!!! It doesn’t matter if everybody you thought would never walk out on you or talk about you… do! You got this! You’re chosen! You matter! The MORE you LIKE YOURSELF the less you’ll need others to! 👊🏼👊🏼👊🏼 now get up, dust yourself off.. be the global world changer that you are created to be! Your best is yet to come! #realtalkkim #comebackkid

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by REAL TALK KIM on July 25, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'I'M CLAIMING LIFE CHANGING MIRACLES for all of us in the next 30 days. www.realtalkkim.com'.

node.text: Everything.. I mean EVERYTHING is changing in your life for the better! Miraculous miracles all around you. REST.. God is going to do some AMAZING things this week. This week is the beginning of the best rest of your life, full of divine appointments, and favor.#realtalkkim

node.text: What are you doing to love your life? What makes you excited? Happy? Feel fulfilled? I pray that you become so filled with happiness that it heals every part of you! It’s time to live your most incredible life ever. LIVE!!!! remember, as long as you aren’t dead… God ain’t done! Let’s GO! Happiness is a choice.. your choice!! #realtalkkim #peace #joy #lifestyle #god #happy

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by REAL TALK KIM on July 24, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'DELETE THE OLD VERSION OF ME INSIDE YOUR HEAD... IT EXPIRED! @realtalkkim'.

node.text: Keep growing through it all. No matter what may hit you. You’re not your past. It doesn’t matter what people label you. They don’t decide your future. People will even label you as hard to deal with when they realize they can't play you. Keep focused! You’re just limited edition! 😬😬

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by REAL TALK KIM on July 23, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'You may feel broken but you're chosen. Rest, God's got you! @RealTalkKim'.

node.text: I decree that you begin to  experience restful sleep like never before. In Jesus name, I break the power of restlessness, sleeplessness, insomnia, tensions, and physical distress that would rob you of a good nights rest. I cast out every nightmare and night terror and I say it cannot operate ever again around you or your home! I speak peace to your mind and body during the night hours. I say that every muscle, bone, sale, organ and hormone must align itself correctly so you are able to rest. I speak peace to the environment around you and say that you operate in God’s promise that he gives his beloved sleep. I speak Sweet sleep upon you and may your nights be restful, comfortable, relaxing, and calm. I say that your nights of sleep shall be the best and most rejuvenating yet! Amen
